lter controls to let users filter agents by project, type, status, and operating stage. Finally, I'll use a premium UI with a dark theme and monospace labels.\n\n\n**Implementing Filter Logic**\n\nI'm now implementing the filter logic based on the user's requirements, specifically addressing filtering by project, agent type, status, and operating stage. I've been reviewing the mock data, particularly `previewAgentOperations` and `previewAgentHealths`. I am implementing project filtering by project ID, including user-friendly names, and extracting the agent type from agent data.\n\n\n\n"}}
